{"id": 760, "genre": 1001, "title": "你看过哪些站在道德高地上说话的人？", "description": "你一直站在道德高地上说话，就不冷吗？——《唐顿庄园》（题图来自：Daniela Gallego）", "record_count": 8041, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194528cHfYLoMREPTzWUlr.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-14T11:33:26Z", "options": [{"id": 41216, "content": "有关部门表示", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256570}, {"id": 41217, "content": "“快打120/110啊”，“哎这些人为什么只围观不帮忙啊”，“如果是我肯定不会……”╮(╯_╰)╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416680}, {"id": 41218, "content": "中国的贫富差距越来越大，贫富之间的矛盾也越来越深。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273373}, {"id": 41219, "content": "去日本就是投降买国，用日货就是汉奸叛徒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 477, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234114}, {"id": 45572, "content": "丑人多作怪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450692}, {"id": 41221, "content": "广电总菊和他的朋友ccav", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004750fAaDpoZXgcKON2ke.jpg", "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354860}, {"id": 41222, "content": "都是为你好…BalaBala", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004853DNMekH1IgwdUlhzp.jpg", "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 365090}, {"id": 41225, "content": "说别人站在高地的人才真正站在高地——鸠尼·缀·午僚", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 351889}, {"id": 41234, "content": "我们都是为你好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404280}, {"id": 41236, "content": "专家说……根据专家统计……专家决定……！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343578}, {"id": 42260, "content": "你们呐，就是幼稚。我走过的桥比你走的路还多！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428413}, {"id": 41240, "content": "乌鲁木齐正在申办全国文明城市…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422649}, {"id": 41242, "content": "践踏别人来夺取道德高地还少了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263224}, {"id": 42015, "content": "做这些事没意义，纯属浪费时间和钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428267}, {"id": 41248, "content": "我是为了你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1931}, {"id": 41251, "content": "我是你爸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391138}, {"id": 41252, "content": "今天是抗战胜利纪念日，你竟然在晒娃", "image": null, "praise_count": 137, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 371344}, {"id": 42280, "content": "我是学法的，学法的人就是有正义感、", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337359}, {"id": 41259, "content": "大家都在庆祝阅兵，你却在晒娃 你不是中国人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 344628}, {"id": 163119, "content": "差不多所有上热评的事，都有，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651741}, {"id": 41264, "content": "这个话题里说别人站道德高地的不也都是么", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141957}, {"id": 41776, "content": "怎么啦……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 297810}, {"id": 41265, "content": "不转必考59", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423120}, {"id": 41266, "content": "不发就是不把我当朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423120}, {"id": 42295, "content": "我这都是为了你好。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277490}, {"id": 42808, "content": "你怎么变了～当初你那么纯真无邪～（谁不是每时每刻都在变化，不过没符合谁的利益罢了）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1201260}, {"id": 41275, "content": "My candle burns at both end ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423201}, {"id": 42299, "content": "我爸和我男友！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429741}, {"id": 41280, "content": "所有人都这个德行，每天都看见圣母婊和喷圣母婊的圣母婊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224517}, {"id": 41281, "content": "现在的年轻人啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391562}, {"id": 41537, "content": "如果我的玩笑让你生气了，对不起。我以为我们很熟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425296}, {"id": 41284, "content": "你作业都做了你不借我抄抄？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117255}, {"id": 42820, "content": "这就是中国和外国的区别", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354986}, {"id": 41285, "content": "阿狸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253513}, {"id": 41286, "content": "神马和什么的身份论证！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265541}, {"id": 41287, "content": "这个世界有几个人不认为自己在道德高地", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423293}, {"id": 41543, "content": "他们做这些事只是因为他们是人，不能怪他们。——《狗镇》", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425288}, {"id": 42311, "content": "全中国人都感动哭了.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324289}, {"id": 44872, "content": "xx那么努力，你知道吗。真想笑，社会如此，谁不努力。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446428}, {"id": 41291, "content": "每天上班12小时，领导还眨巴着白花花的眼仁儿说：要讲奉献，讲牺牲", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417972}, {"id": 41292, "content": "你知道他在台下有多努力么", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153707}, {"id": 41293, "content": "你说什么 他都说 你别站在道德的制高点上抨击我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423304}, {"id": 41296, "content": "你真的爱我就不该嫌我穷而一再犹豫不决", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200836KA1Pw0ShqRorfGpF.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 45835}, {"id": 41808, "content": "唉算了，说了你也不明白", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 427147}, {"id": 41297, "content": "有时候都会的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423321}, {"id": 41298, "content": "你看看某某家的孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 384146}, {"id": 41554, "content": "天下男人一样黑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224481}, {"id": 46162, "content": "为了家人健康你就转吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 445647}, {"id": 41043, "content": "你们就是为富不仁，开个跑车必定是为富不仁，开个超市也一定是为富不仁", "image": null, "praise_count": 301, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 41299, "content": "你那么厉害为什么不XX", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 384146}]}